    "basmil_image_text_xRzLJX": {
      "type": "basmil-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "content_tzFbBg": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How to Enjoy Himalayan Mad Honey?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>The Himalayan honey is versatile and can be enjoyed any time of day, whether you start your morning with a spoonful or use it to unwind later. We recommend our users to follow the standard serving size and for all the new users, start with a small dose and increase gradually until reaching the recommended serving size.</p><p><strong>Raw</strong><br/>Enjoy a small spoonful directly to experience its bold, earthy, floral flavor. New customers should begin with a small serving to understand personal sensitivity.</p><p><strong>Tea and Drinks<br/></strong>You can upgrade your mad honey experience by mixing it with your favorite non-alcoholic beverages. Try it in warm water, or tea, or blend it into a healthy smoothie for a unique twist.</p><p><strong>Dishes and Desserts<br/></strong><a href=\"https://medicinalmadhoney.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mad honey\">Mad honey</a> can make a go-to natural sweetener, its use can make any dishes or desserts delightful. Remember not to expose it to heat beyond 118° F or 48° C as this may degrade heat-sensitive nutrients. Using this as a topping, drizzle, mixing it into smoothies or adding it to low-heat desserts works best.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text_2": "",
            "button_link_2": ""
          }
        },
        "image_UKXN96": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_type": "image",
