    "faq_fFAwqm": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_XEPM9x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is Himalayan mad honey?",
            "answer": "<p>Himalayan mad honey is a natural, specialty honey from cliffside hives at high mountain altitudes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bJtL4k": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where does your mad honey come from?",
            "answer": "<p>Medicinal mad honey comes from the mountainous cliffs of Nepal.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_cU9Bya": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is mad honey the same as regular honey?",
            "answer": "<p>No, mad honey is not the same as regular honey. The differences mainly come down to remote origin, traditional harvesting and limited availability.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_RHLdYj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What does mad honey taste like?",
            "answer": "<p>Mad honey tastes sweet and has a deep and intense flavor profile.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_B7TK9g": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What serving size should beginners start with?",
            "answer": "<p>If you’re a beginner, start with a small serving, such as a small teaspoon, to understand personal sensitivity. <br/>Because mad honey is a unique wild honey with naturally occurring grayanotoxin, it should be used responsibly and in moderation.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_UzHYFV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How should beginners enjoy mad honey?",
            "answer": "<p>Beginners can enjoy a small amount directly or mix it into warm drinks, yogurt, toast, or light desserts. Start small and avoid overuse.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_6JXXi9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Who should avoid mad honey?",
            "answer": "<p>Mad honey is not recommended for children, pregnant or breastfeeding women. Also, people with heart problems or under medication should take suggestions from their General Practitioner before beginning the consumption.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_3UNgd6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Why is mad honey rare?",
            "answer": "<p>Mad honey is rare because it is harvested seasonally. The maker bees themselves are limited to high altitudes, Himalayan flowers bloom only two times a year and the hives are built only in limited mountain cliffs. The extraction from towering cliffs is also difficult- everything combined makes mad honey rare.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_3WGxp3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you have retail store locations?",
            "answer": "<p>No. We operate exclusively online to serve customers worldwide directly from our source.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_AiBaE3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you have active discount codes or promotions?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. First-time customers receive 10% off their first order. We also offer special discounts and seasonal promotions during different occassions throughout the year.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_Xe6Q6N": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How can I contact customer service?",
            "answer": "<p>If you have inquiries or want to collaborate, feel free to contact us at: contact@medicinalmadhoney.com</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_izzk3i": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer express shipping?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Express shipping options are available for selected destinations. We generally deliver your order within a minimum of two days minimum while this time may extend depending on the destination country and customs clearance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_MXxDWK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you ship internationally?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. We ship internationally to customers across multiple countries using delivery services like DHL Express, Aramex and Fedex.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_g3fLhz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer free shipping?",
            "answer": "<p>All of our services, retail or wholesale, are exclusive of free shipping. In some countries, import duties, customs charges or VAT may also apply which are beyond our control and remain the responsibility of the customer.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
