            "title": "Pure Honey, Pure Intention",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>We’re all about ethical, sustainable practices. Our mad honey is hand-harvested by skilled beekeepers in remote regions, so you get only the best. We try our best to be environmentally responsible in every step from sourcing to packaging. We’re committed to supporting local communities and protecting the environment where this special honey is found.</p>",
